title: Primesoft Web Builder Deluxe v2.7
description:
Overview
Web Builder Deluxe is a Windows software that allows individuals, small businesses, and corporations to organize and manage virtually any kind of structured data on your desktop PC. Web Builder&#039;s HTML publishing capability allows you to quickly create webready catalogs, directories that you can publish on your Internet site. Web Builder&#039;s integration with our Web dB Server application allows you to put your databases on the Internet. They are right away ready for online processing.
